00:46:16.000 --> 00:46:20.000
which they just say it has not
escaped our notice that this model

00:46:20.000 --> 00:46:24.000
explains replication and everything
else. Basically the last sentence

00:46:24.000 --> 00:46:28.000
says, oh, and by the way, it
has not escaped our notice that

00:46:28.000 --> 00:46:31.000
this explains the secret of life.
Although, it didn't say it like that.

00:46:31.000 --> 00:46:35.000
It's the coyest sentence in
