00:46:45.000 --> 00:46:49.000
So, you will hear molecular
biologists make reference,

00:46:49.000 --> 00:46:52.000
use in their speech the phrase,
it has not escaped our notice that.

00:46:52.000 --> 00:46:56.000
And it's always a homage back to
this particular sentence in this

00:46:56.000 --> 00:46:59.000
paper of Crick and Watson.
OK, now, last thing. Yes?

